citation.case_name: Harris v. Florida Real Estate Comm'n

html:
371 U.S. 7

83 S.Ct. 19

9 L.Ed.2d 47

Milton J. HARRIS
v.
FLORIDA REAL ESTATE COMM'N, etc., et al.

No. 100.

Supreme Court of the United States

October 8, 1962

Rehearing Denied Nov. 13, 1962.

See 371 U.S. 906, 83 S.Ct. 203.

M. H. Rosenhouse, for appellant.

Benjamin T. Shuman, for appellees.

PER CURIAM.

1

The motion to dismiss is granted and the appeal is dismissed. Treating the papers whereon the appeal was taken as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.

2

Mr. Justice GOLDBERG took no part in the consideration or decision of this case.
